 To create files
we can create files by two commands 
•	touch
•	cat
To create a empty file we use 
touch filename
to add some data in file while creating a file
cat >filename
after entering the data we want press
CTRL+d to save the data

To edit the file 
vi filename
to edit the saved file we can also use 
cat >> filename

To count the words in a file
wc filename
to count the lines 
wc –l filename
